{
  "texts": [
    "A comprehensive and systematic search was conducted using Wisenews.",
    "The search was restricted to \"Hong Kong Media\", under the news feature of Education, dated between 1 December 2022 to 31 July 2023.",
    "Since \"ChatGPT\" is commonly used in both Chinese and English newspapers in Hong Kong, it is the only search term for this study and 272 articles were identified.The authors then screened away any news articles that were not focused on local public universities or ChatGPT.",
    "Additionally, news columns were not included because they are less objective than news reports and even if the writers are academics, they may not entirely represent the stands of the university.",
    "By the end of this stage, 27 articles were left."
  ]
}